thread.title: BRIEF-Alliances FY Consolidated Net Income Up At 251 Million Dirhams

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Alliances FY Consolidated Net Income Up At 251 Million Dirhams
text:
March 30 (Reuters) - ALLIANCES DEVELOPPEMENT IMMOBILIERE STE SA:
* FY CONSOLIDATED REVENUE MAD 3.02 BILLION VERSUS MAD 3.56 BILLION YEAR AGO‍​‍​
* FY CONSOLIDATED NET INCOME MAD 251 MILLION VERSUS MAD 178 MILLION YEAR AGO
* NET DEBT AT END-DEC MAD 4.7 BILLION VERSUS MAD 5.2 BILLION AT END-JUNE
* SEES NET DEBT AT END-DEC 2018 AT MAD 2 BILLION
* CONFIRMS OUTLOOK FOR GROWTH AND ACTIVITY IN 2018 * SEES REDUCTION OF FINANCIAL EXPENSES TO ABOUT MAD 100 MILLION IN 2018 Source text: bit.ly/2uFj935 Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
